➜桂阳浩塘镇鲤鱼村：最后一名贫困户脱贫摘帽
http://www.sohu.com/a/424231555_100180399	3089
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/23c15679ba874ce78a6fd9eb55ce77dd.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">彭三崽的养殖事业。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/2284a53e920f495496fbaa25662531f7.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">彭三崽的收入来源。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/2f9135be2d924830bfaf7bab78a3e890.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
